pageProduct.name: Rite Aid Nursing Pads 72 Pack
pageProduct.description:
General Information

Rite Aid Nursing pads are the discreet, leak-proof system to keep you dry between feeds, while breastfeeding.

The breathable honeycomb lining allows for quick moisture absorption for a confident and dry feeling day and night.  The super soft 3D moulded pad enhanced by elastic edges is designed for a natural fit to keep you comfortable.

Warnings

Use only as indicated.  Keep out of reach of children.

Common Uses

Rite Aid Nursing Pads protect breastfeeding mums against breast milk leakage.

Ingredients

- Non-woven
- Super Absorbent Polymer (SAP)

Directions

It is recommended that you change your nursing pads frequently as breast milk is rich in nutrients and can cause bacteria at room temperature.
